Let’s try out the @loverecode we stole da show intense gel eyeliners today! I have it in 3 shades, Carbon black, Coffee brown & Sensational white. 
The product contains 5gms and retails for ₹.655 and it’s manufactured in Taiwan. 
Coming to the product, it’s rich and intense and extremely pigmented. The product is very creamy to use and easy to apply. It glides smoothly on the lid and it’s very helpful to create thin lines too without creasing. I love using these to create everyday eyeliner looks and you can take it up to a graphic eyeliner and it also doubles up as a brow pomade too. 
These are some of the best eyeliners and it’s extremely intense too! Try it out and I hope you all love it too !! 🥰🥰🥰
